24 BEHAVIORAL HEALTH AUTHORITY FOR THE MISUSE OF ALCOHOL AND DRUGS.
25 (3) THE PRINCE GEORGE’S COUNTY HEALTH DEPARTMENT SHALL
26 ADMINISTER THE FUND.
27 (4) (I) THE FUND IS A SPECIAL CONTINUING, NONLAPSING FUND
28 THAT IS NOT SUBJECT TO § 7–302 OF THE STATE FINANCE AND PROCUREMENT
29 ARTICLE.

